description:
In this coding challenge, I attempt recreate a 3D @beesandbombs GIF with p5.js and the WebGL renderer.

🤖GIF: https://twitter.com/beesandbombs/status/940639806522085376

💻Challenge: https://thecodingtrain.com/CodingChallenges/086-beesandbombs.html

🔗p5.js reference: https://p5js.org/reference/

🎥Simple Harmonic Motion: https://youtu.be/GvwPwIUSYqE
